{"tid":1157313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賊仔出胡椒噴劑劫沙浦道7仔搶走一包煙　重案接手調查","createTime":"2019-05-16T07:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T11:07:34.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c9cc2af9db233b9790caf47116dda54b6208aded","tid":1157313,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T07:52:03.000Z","msg":"九龍城沙浦道46號一間7-11便利店，今日(16日)早上8時許，一名年約30歲男子，突然衝入店內，手持胡椒噴劑指嚇收銀櫃位2名姓曾(37歲)及姓譚(23歲)男職員，並且向對方一輪狂噴，譚閃避不及，被胡椒噴劑噴中。期間，賊人迅速擸走櫃內一盒香煙後，即奪門逃去，職員驚魂甫定後報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報到場，在附近一帶兜截無果，將案件暫列盜竊案，交由黃大仙警區重案組跟進，正進一步翻看附近「天眼」錄影片段，追緝涉案竊賊人歸案。他身高約1.75米，案發時身穿白色上衣、藍色外套及深色褲。<br />\n<br />\n該便利店屢次發生劫案，去年1月8日，一名戴眼鏡男賊闖入並亮刀指嚇姓何（36歲）男職員，逼其打開收銀機，掠走機內約3500港元現金後逃去。另外，17年11月9日凌晨，一名𠝹刀賊闖入指嚇一名姓譚(22歲)男職員擸走約8000港元現金逃去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190516/bkn-20190516091955641-0516_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190516%2Fbkn-20190516091955641-0516_00822_001.html&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf%2FzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=218ed0bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190516/bkn-20190516091955641-0516_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c7cac006455abfb8d6e1c99987ee3e2d58783840","tid":1157313,"uid":126866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"一包<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26cd90d8f91cd3109dc7bd55c23c2695a51d15b","tid":1157313,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T07:55:01.000Z","msg":"宜家啲賊真係冇大志"},{"pid":"9275beb910fb39b7a68c9c636cac7c4610e8f132","tid":1157313,"uid":159236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"你支噴劑成本分分鐘貴過包煙，仲有比人拉嘅風險。係咪玩緊炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd064bdaeb7573dc6200f3381ac00411b73ee58","tid":1157313,"uid":280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"條友試武器....岩岩整好..試下威力得唔得...<br />\n遲下打劫"},{"pid":"6393837271fd03ceb7b14ab435797d71b3f906dd","tid":1157313,"uid":96877,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"姓譚嗰個比人搶左兩次仲係到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0f047873c32f423f07ba7480ed68d39a6678c1","tid":1157313,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6393837271fd03ceb7b14ab435797d71b3f906dd","tid":1157313,"uid":96877,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"姓譚嗰個比人搶左兩次仲係到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T07:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b114ec975b833d6499cc98733e0bb4b2fedb0d","tid":1157313,"uid":34935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6393837271fd03ceb7b14ab435797d71b3f906dd","tid":1157313,"uid":96877,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"姓譚嗰個比人搶左兩次仲係到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:01:12.000Z","msg":"內應黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad59de723050ac03e97f4c10a62276f13a0fa2a","tid":1157313,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae0f047873c32f423f07ba7480ed68d39a6678c1","tid":1157313,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6393837271fd03ceb7b14ab435797d71b3f906dd","tid":1157313,"uid":96877,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"姓譚嗰個比人搶左兩次仲係到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T07:59:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos